 of detection accuracy,\nfalse positive or negative rate and energy consumption while also keeping\nacceptable network performance such as improved detection latency and at par\npacket delivery ratio.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2020 19:42:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-30"}
