er. Regressing the\nstorage time of the eggs, tests achieved a coefficient of determination\n(R-squared) of $0.8319\\pm0.0377$ and a root mean squared error (RMSE) of 1.97.\n  Although further work is needed, this technique has shown industrial\npotential and consumer utility to determine the egg's freshness by using a\nlow-cost spectrometer connected to a smartphone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2020 09:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-30"}
